You understand that there will hardly be such people anymore.

553
00:34:29,372 --> 00:34:30,600
Unfortunately.

554
00:34:30,600 --> 00:34:31,776
Unfortunately.

555
00:34:31,901 --> 00:34:33,300
Because all those who ...

