569
00:35:09,814 --> 00:35:10,526
Really?

570
00:35:10,551 --> 00:35:11,399
Yes.

571
00:35:14,541 --> 00:35:15,265
Is he lying?

572
00:35:15,289 --> 00:35:16,876
It is all true.

573
00:35:18,589 --> 00:35:22,302
The war two years ago and the war now.

574
00:35:24,785 --> 00:35:25,831
It's different.

575
00:35:30,350 --> 00:35:33,124
The enemy is also making conclusions.

576
00:35:33,795 --> 00:35:35,555
Trying to improve.

577
00:35:38,415 --> 00:35:40,146
Not standing still.

578
00:35:40,208 --> 00:35:51,598
Tell me... I'm sorry for the formulation, is there now
a tough technical war, without hatred towards them?

579
00:35:52,240 --> 00:35:53,988
Well, like in the computer game?

580
00:35:54,013 --> 00:35:55,277
Just killing or ...

581
00:35:55,302 --> 00:35:56,302
I will speak for myself.

582
00:35:56,326 --> 00:35:57,976
or do you hate them?

583
00:35:59,385 --> 00:36:01,385
Well, hatred...

584
00:36:04,466 --> 00:36:14,496
