it as long as I have enough strength and health.

585
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:16,000
I just do it.

586
00:36:16,000 --> 00:36:17,916
Hate? Well, and there is hate, yes.

587
00:36:17,941 --> 00:36:19,689
Why? I don't know...

588
00:36:19,714 --> 00:36:29,000
My parents worked faithfully hard to
earn money, built a house, acquired something.

589
00:36:29,000 --> 00:36:34,873
At any moment, a rocket can just fly into
my house, and that's it, it won't be there.

590
00:36:34,898 --> 00:36:38,000
I have a father from the Donetsk region,

591
00:36:38,521 --> 00:36:43,000
