They love it terribly at their homes.

994
01:02:29,489 --> 01:02:37,418
Language, faith, church, and you know, everyone is kissing,
and as a result, we have corrupt people in Vyshyvankas.

995
01:02:37,443 --> 01:02:39,751
Yes, it is so.

996
01:02:39,776 --> 01:02:41,895
I forgot to ask,

997
01:02:41,920 --> 01:02:45,920
you said that you wanted to go to the unblocking, right?

998
01:02:45,945 --> 01:02:50,895
When the guys came out and you looked
at these shots, what did you think?

999
01:02:51,208 --> 01:02:52,920
What were your feelings then?

1000
01:02:52,920 --> 01:02:54,920
Well, it hurt a lot.

1001
01:02:54,920 --> 01:02:56,920
It must have been a feeling of compassion.

1002
01:02:57,643 --> 01:03:07,761
I understood why it happened. Because it was necessary
to help the heavily wounded or they would have just died.

1003
01:03:09,253 --> 01:03:11,253
They would've died.

1004
01:03:11,566 --> 01:03:12,920
Everyone understood.

1005
01:03:12,920 --> 01:03:14,657
It was just hard to understand.

1006
01:03:14,682 --> 01:03:23,740
Even, well, I think that even civilians
understand that our enemy cannot be trusted.

1007
01:03:23,765 --> 01:03:31,920
The pre-agreements according to which they came out,
were not, unfortunately, fulfilled by them.

1008
01:03:31,920 --> 01:03:35,655
No third party would lift a finger.

1009
01:03:36,920 --> 01:03:52,259
I was 90% sure that it was for washing the eyes, to show, from their side,
that they still have some kind of military honor, some military rules of war.

1010
01:03:53,481 --> 01:04:01,219
In fact, we have seen, we see it to this day,
how they behave and what they do there.

1011
01:04:01,477 --> 01:04:11,323
That's why further negotiations, it's a joke.

1012
01:04:11,947 --> 01:04:13,920
So how will this war end?

1013
01:04:15,390 --> 01:04:25,099
I think it will end sooner or later with our victory,
but it should end on their territory.

1014
01:04:27,696 --> 01:04:30,920
When our army will be there.

1015
01:04:31,845 --> 01:04:37,431
When we can impose on them our conditions, then we will win.

1016
01:04:41,920 --> 01:04:44,577
This is, well, like, this is my subjective opinion.

1017
01:04:44,602 --> 01:04:46,920
Well, there is war mathematics.
There are fewer of us.

1018
01:04:47,800 --> 01:04:48,546
Yes, there are fewer of us.

1019
01:04:48,571 --> 01:04:50,777
So, in this decision, something needs to be corrected.

1020
01:04:50,802 --> 01:04:52,548
Well, if...

1021
01:04:53,920 --> 01:04:56,920
There hasn't been such a turning point yet.

1022
01:04:56,920 --> 01:04:58,543
It hasn't happened yet.

1023
01:04:58,568 --> 01:05:00,269
It will happen someday.

1024
01:05:00,294 --> 01:05:05,790
It will happen, no matter how many there are of us and them.

1025
01:05:07,244 --> 01:05:09,633
According to the number of the army.

1026
01:05:09,658 --> 01:05:14,200
When this moment comes, it will stop working.

1027
01:05:14,920 --> 01:05:29,031
Already during the full-scale war, I think that our army has already proven
this many times and shown that the number does not always matter.

1028
01:05:29,559 --> 01:05:41,111
If we use our strength correctly and effectively, use the weapons
that we are given, I hope that they keep giving it to us, help us,

1029
01:05:41,812 --> 01:05:54,104
and not hold us on this leash, and our unit in general, which
is not provided with Western weapons and equipment at all.

1030
01:05:54,920 --> 01:05:56,594
And then, if we do all this...

1031
01:05:56,619 --> 01:05:59,501
Do you not have Western or American weapons?

1032
01:05:59,526 --> 01:06:01,526
We have ...

1033
01:06:01,551 --> 01:06:03,012
Or is this war secret?

1034
01:06:03,037 --> 01:06:04,037
Okay, that's it.

1035
01:06:04,062 --> 01:06:06,395
We may already have it, but only from the state.

1036
01:06:06,537 --> 01:06:08,157
Not from the state?

1037
01:06:08,182 --> 01:06:08,997
Yes.

1038
01:06:09,022 --> 01:06:11,511
Well, from volunteers and good people.

1039
01:06:13,920 --> 01:06:23,541
Although, our higher management has already asked,
what else we have to do to be given it.

1040
01:06:23,566 --> 01:06:24,723
What else to prove?

1041
01:06:24,748 --> 01:06:27,531
I want to say to the viewers that we will also have a fundraising.

1042
01:06:27,556 --> 01:06:29,895
This fundraising will be for the Azov brigade.

1043
01:06:29,920 --> 01:06:34,403
The only thing is that now I can't say whether it
will be for medical needs or for military needs.

1044
01:06:34,428 --> 01:06:40,083
Because I will talk to your management
and we will already decide with them.

1045
01:06:40,920 --> 01:06:45,920
It was said by the youth about the picture of the end of the war.

1046
01:06:45,920 --> 01:06:47,586
And now wisdom will speak.

1047
01:06:47,611 --> 01:06:48,231
Yes.

1048
01:06:48,256 --> 01:06:49,256
What?

1049
01:06:49,573 --> 01:06:50,573
Ask.

1050
01:06:51,166 --> 01:06:53,366
What do you see as the end of the war?

1051
01:06:53,391 --> 01:06:54,920
Of course, our victory.

1052
01:06:54,920 --> 01:06:57,920
We will do everything for this.

1053
01:06:57,920 --> 01:06:58,920
Everything.

1054
01:06:59,435 --> 01:07:01,920
Beginning with a soldier to an officer.

1055
01:07:03,423 --> 01:07:04,704
And we are doing everything for this

1056
01:07:04,729 --> 01:07:05,920
and we keep doing.

1057
01:07:05,920 --> 01:07:07,506
As I said earlier.

1058
01:07:07,531 --> 01:07:10,423
As long as we have enough strength

1059
01:07:11,312 --> 01:07:13,920
we will not give up.

1060
01:07:17,899 --> 01:07:27,488
Honestly, sometimes I get tired, let's say, morally.

1061
01:07:27,920 --> 01:07:35,895
But I tell you, I have enough motivation for a long time.

1062
01:07:36,535 --> 01:07:38,391
When will you cut your hair, Iraq?

1063
01:07:38,416 --> 01:07:45,423
I will cut my hair after we are withdrawn from this direction.

1064
01:07:45,448 --> 01:07:47,105
Then I will cut my hair.

1065
01:07:50,565 --> 01:07:51,920
This is some kind of ...

1066
01:07:51,920 --> 01:07:54,450
Well, my superstitions.

1067
01:07:56,052 --> 01:08:07,949
During some period I determined for myself, I do not cut my hair.

1068
01:08:09,307 --> 01:08:12,720
Well, I hope that you will soon see a friend with a haircut.

1069
01:08:12,720 --> 01:08:14,013
He has already cut himself.

1070
01:08:14,038 --> 01:08:18,557
He already sends me photos and says, this is how I want it.

1071
01:08:18,582 --> 01:08:19,920
So that you cut your hair.

1072
01:08:19,920 --> 01:08:20,920
Yes, yes.

1073
01:08:20,944 --> 01:08:22,015
So that he looked like a human.

1074
01:08:22,039 --> 01:08:23,659
Thank you very much.

1075
01:08:23,684 --> 01:08:24,920
Thank you for this conversation.

1076
01:08:24,945 --> 01:08:26,895
Thank you for the interview.

1077
01:08:26,920 --> 01:08:27,920
Thank you.

1078
01:08:28,631 --> 01:08:29,540
I just came.

1079
01:08:29,565 --> 01:08:33,524
Hello. My name is Ilya.
Brigade Azov. National Guard of Ukraine.

1080
01:08:33,549 --> 01:08:35,540
Oh, Azov. Cool. Let's work.

1081
01:08:35,565 --> 01:08:36,334
Okay, good.

1082
01:08:36,359 --> 01:08:38,022
By the way, we are not Nazis.

1083
01:08:39,543 --> 01:08:42,826
Oh. Yes. I understood. Yes.

1084
01:08:43,175 --> 01:08:48,508
Well, society expects that the next day,
after the end of the war, there will be elections.

1085
01:08:48,533 --> 01:08:55,918
Therefore, all the soldiers whom they love, value,
and who they`re grateful to, will come to the Verkhovna Rada.

1086
01:08:55,943 --> 01:08:56,943
Expecting.

1087
01:08:57,364 --> 01:08:58,086
They want.

1088
01:08:58,111 --> 01:08:59,735
Not just the Verkhovna Rada.

1089
01:08:59,760 --> 01:09:03,537
Then again, there are wishes and there are reality.

1090
01:09:03,562 --> 01:09:04,840
Are they wanting you in the politics?

1091
01:09:04,865 --> 01:09:05,865
Well, yes.

1092
01:09:05,890 --> 01:09:09,409
Those people who bribe very often act like a puppeteer.

1093
01:09:09,434 --> 01:09:09,831
Well yes.

1094
01:09:09,856 --> 01:09:13,928
I do not like such people and I am very suspicious of them.

1095
01:09:13,953 --> 01:09:19,100
Does the front line now look like it is in a positional impasse?

1096
